data.description: REDUCED PRICE! This 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom with laminate flooring at Hill n Dale home is ready for a new owner! Live in the Country but be close to the Big City!! The home sits on just under a 1/2 acre/double lot.  This Lovely Back Yard is Perfect for the Family to Play Soccer or Football and for the Dogs to Run Outside too or build a NEW HOME.  FENCED back yard with Chain Link Fencing with a large carport, workshop/garage, SHED included. Inside Laundry Room with Washer and Dryer That Do Stay with the Home.  Its Located Close to Parks, Schools, Shopping, Dining and Just Minutes from the I-75 and SR 50 Exit. And its Only 10 Minutes From Beautiful, Historic Downtown Brooksville. Close to the Suncoast for an easy commute to Tampa.  This House is Perfect for the First Time Home Buyer or for the Investor who Would like a Wonderful Rental Property. This home is truly move in perfect with NEW ROOF changed & updated electrical box (4 years ago), NEW HVAC (5 years ago)
